 Thursday . August 19th . 1915 Dear Nell , I enlist today and I have bought this book to make a diari , dure the time I am away at the front . I hope to get away soon for I am go into camp straight away , so I intend to start it off the day I sail , so that , from that day on you will have an account of what I did in the Great War . Your love Brother Harri
